text: The Justice League Dark is a fictional superhero team featured in the DC Comics. The team debuted in Justice League Dark #1 (September 2011) and was created by Peter Milligan. It is a team that is filled with Justice League's supernatural world. Justice League Dark originally featured John Constantine, Madame Xanadu, Deadman, Shade the Changing Man, and Zatanna, eventually being joined by prominent members such as Swamp Thing and Wonder Woman.
